{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Public Inquiry into the effectiveness of the DWP in relation to disabled people.",
        "additional_details": "Following the BBC Panorama program which showed how some staff at the DWP are treated and how some decision makers behave, I believe the DWP is not fit for purpose when it comes to deciding benefits for disabled people or even employing disabled people.",
        "background": "We demand a public inquiry into the way the DWP deals with disabled people, both within the DWP and with those who seek benefit assistance from the DWP.",
